           <h1><strong>20 VIC Online Privacy Policy</strong></h1>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>By accessing or using the 20 VIC Website, you agree to the terms of the 20 VIC Online Privacy Policy, as outlined below. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not access or use this site. 20 VIC reserves the right to change the Online Privacy Policy from time to time at its sole discretion. Your use of this site will be subject to the most current version of the Online Privacy Policy at the time of such use.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Cookies</strong></p>

<p>A &quot;cookie&quot; is a piece of data stored on the user&#39;s hard drive, containing information about the user. We do not use cookies at this time on our site, but if we were to use cookies, none of them contain any personally identifiable information. Some of our business partners use cookies on their sites. You may choose not to accept cookies by setting your browser to refuse all cookies or to notify you each time a cookie is set. If you choose to refuse cookies, however, you may not be able to use all features of our site in the future.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Surveys &amp; Contests</strong></p>

<p>From time-to-time our site requests information from users via surveys or contests. Participation in these surveys or contests is completely voluntary and the user therefore has a choice whether or not to disclose this information. Information requested may include contact information (such as name and e‑mail addresses), and demographic information (such as postal code, age level and addresses). We do not sell this information. 20 VIC will use the information submitted on the ballot for our marketing purposes.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>E-Newsletters</strong></p>

<p>Email newsletters are sent out only to users who choose to provide us with their email address. By providing your email address and subscribing to our database you have agreed to receive newsletters from us. Our subscriber&#39;s database is never sold, rented or loaned to any other parties. Subscribers wishing to opt-out from receiving newsletters can do so at any time.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Security</strong></p>


<p>20 VIC uses industry standard technology and efforts to safeguard the confidentiality of your personal identifiable information. These include secure servers and firewalls. All of the user data we collect is protected against unauthorized access. Only authorized employees who need the information to perform a specific job are granted access to this information.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Notification of Changes</strong></p>

<p>We are always improving and updating our Website to further enhance your shopping experience. As a result, our policies will continue to evolve. As we implement new technology and provide new services, we will update our Privacy Policy. We encourage you to refer to this page on an ongoing basis for our most current policy and practices.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Third Party Links</strong></p>

<p>Our site sometimes provides links to Websites that are operated solely by third parties that are not under our control. This Privacy Statement applies to our site only, and is not intended to describe the privacy policies of any third party sites.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Updating your personal information</strong></p>

<p>You have the right to access and correct your personal information and privacy preferences at any time.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Privacy related complaints</strong></p>

<p>If you believe that 20 VIC not complied with this Online Privacy Policy with respect to your personal information, please call us at 416 955-0569. If you prefer to write, please notify us at: </p>

<p>Privacy Concerns, One Queen Street E., Suite 300, Box #88, Toronto, Ontario, M5C 2W5</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>In your letter, please describe in as much detail as possible the ways in which you believe that 20 VIC&#39;s Online Privacy Policy has not been complied with. We will investigate your complaint promptly.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>Please note that if you provide this 20 VIC Website with inconsistent privacy preferences (for example, by indicating on one occasion that third parties may contact you with marketing offers and indicating on another occasion that they may not), 20 VIC cannot guarantee that your most recent privacy preference will be honored.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>Also, please note that 20 VIC is not responsible for the content or privacy practices of non-20 VIC Websites to which 20 VIC related third party Website may link to.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>Thank you for visiting this 20 VIC Website.</p>

